casebody.data:
Collignor, Appellant, v. Miller, Respondent. (Supreme Court,General Term, Fifth Department. June 22, 1889.)

Argued before Barker, P. J., and Dwight and Maoomber, JJ.

No opinion. Order of special term reversed, with $10 costs and disbursements, on the ground that the court had no power to make such order.
